room_title: Escape room "Timewarp Escape" by Timewarp Escape in Denver
room_description: For 60 minutes or less, your team is warped back to the 1980's via sights and sounds. From hacking into a Commodore 64 computer to dressing in neon and playing with toys from the golden age of games - this room escape experience bridges retro technology and nostalgia in an entirely innovative way.
